{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"d3wtpb7sfakjqrh6f0uliif","title":"Shen","desc":"","updated":1691811072088,"created":1691808058569,"custom":{},"fname":"life.belief.bazi.shen","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"repos/dendron-aws-vault","remote":{"type":"git","url":"https://github.com/cczhong11/my_note.git"},"name":"my_note"},"contentHash":"6849fe464390a0f19ee1d25f0d429e80","links":[{"from":{"fname":"life.belief.bazi.shishen.geju","id":"2ejnehom1dpe6ac3aoez1zn","vaultName":"my_note"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":43,"column":1,"offset":637},"end":{"line":43,"column":26,"offset":662},"indent":[]},"value":"life.belief.bazi.shen"}],"anchors":{"扶抑用神":{"type":"header","text":"扶抑用神","value":"扶抑用神","line":8,"column":0,"depth":2},"调候用神":{"type":"header","text":"调候用神","value":"调候用神","line":15,"column":0,"depth":2},"格局用神":{"type":"header","text":"格局用神","value":"格局用神","line":19,"column":0,"depth":2},"什么是顺用":{"type":"header","text":"什么是“顺用”？","value":"什么是顺用","line":29,"column":0,"depth":3},"如何应用顺用":{"type":"header","text":"如何应用“顺用”？","value":"如何应用顺用","line":33,"column":0,"depth":3},"什么是逆用":{"type":"header","text":"什么是“逆用”？","value":"什么是逆用","line":38,"column":0,"depth":3},"如何应用逆用":{"type":"header","text":"如何应用“逆用”？","value":"如何应用逆用","line":42,"column":0,"depth":3}},"children":[],"parent":"911z8xyusnfmzgoq2oz1la5","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"shen\">Shen<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#shen\"></a></h1>\n<h2 id=\"扶抑用神\">扶抑用神<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#扶抑用神\"></a></h2>\n<p>它的功能是帮助命局恢复平衡。因为它涉及命局的日主强弱问题，这类“用神”也就称为“扶抑用神。</p>\n<p>扶抑策略:衰者宜扶，强者宜抑，过强者宜泄</p>\n<h2 id=\"调候用神\">调候用神<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#调候用神\"></a></h2>\n<p><img src=\"/assets/images/2023-08-11-19-44-17.png\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"格局用神\">格局用神<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#格局用神\"></a></h2>\n<p>看这个用神怎么和格局联系起来，帮助日主。</p>\n<p>如何处理七杀：对于七杀这个“凶神”，最好的方法是“制”或“化”。如果日主自身较强而七杀旺，最宜用食神来制约七杀；如果自身弱而七杀旺，则应见印星（正印或偏印），用印来化杀而生身，即用“化”的手段，让七杀生印，印生自身，从而取得平衡。</p>\n<p>在水（七杀）和日主火之间的木（正印、偏印）可以担任“化”杀功能。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/assets/images/2023-08-11-20-22-47.png\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"什么是顺用\">什么是“顺用”？<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#什么是顺用\"></a></h3>\n<p>“顺用”是指在八字分析中，选择与主导格局相生的五行作为用神，而不主张采取制约的手段。这是一种顺应格局内在性质的方法，强调和谐和平衡。</p>\n<h3 id=\"如何应用顺用\">如何应用“顺用”？<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#如何应用顺用\"></a></h3>\n<p>对于正官格、正财格、偏财格、印格（主要是指正印格）和食神格，在选择用神时，主要寻找顺生的五行。\n不主张采取制约的手段。如果出现制约，常被认为是“破格”。</p>\n<h3 id=\"什么是逆用\">什么是“逆用”？<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#什么是逆用\"></a></h3>\n<p>“逆用”是指在八字分析中，选择与主导格局相制约（烈制）的五行作为用神。与“顺用”强调和谐相生不同，“逆用”采取的是制约的手段。</p>\n<h3 id=\"如何应用逆用\">如何应用“逆用”？<a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#如何应用逆用\"></a></h3>\n<p>对于七杀格、伤官格、偏印格和劫刃格，在选择用神时，可以采取“制约”的手段。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/assets/images/2023-08-11-20-30-16.png\"></p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/2ejnehom1dpe6ac3aoez1zn\">Geju (my_note)</a></li>\n</ul>","noteIndex":{"id":"0f1b48c7-3a25-4016-83a5-15864d7803ad","title":"Development","vault":{"fsPath":"repos/dendron-aws-vault","remote":{"type":"git","url":"https://github.com/cczhong11/my_note.git"},"name":"my_note"},"type":"note","desc":"","links":[{"from":{"fname":"root","id":"c95dc4f5-23db-45e7-a15b-64582a183ccc","vaultName":"my_note"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":8,"column":3,"offset":63},"end":{"line":8,"column":21,"offset":81},"indent":[]},"value":"development"}],"anchors":{},"fname":"development","updated":1618381238346,"created":1612940782409,"parent":null,"children":["400115e9-30f7-4a13-9776-db059bc9cd42","xsX5v3ZsyJ0i6gf9","1bc3b45a-b6f4-4150-87d3-5bd5b6eb8c24","6cea4852-6e7c-4140-b476-85c07b48a642","a40ef849-d301-4d74-a778-e6d9469dfb5d","09d9081f-3dff-453d-8488-7d2344cc8895","p11phg7nb10yw0wck1fyagq","92917ea3-452e-48dc-875e-5cd0002041db","2e151826-cb22-4d89-8ce0-71dad7204ce8","baa39444